column_description: A unique identifier for each poker player in the table
A foreign key that links to the 'people' table, identifying the person associated with the poker player
The number of times the player has reached the final table in poker tournaments
The player's best finish position in poker tournaments (e.g., 1st, 2nd, 3rd)
The player's rank based on their earnings in poker tournaments
The total earnings of the player from poker tournaments
